organizationId.description:
OrganizationID is the owner organization for a custom language;
nil for shared languages. Useful for callers that need to display
the source of the language ("from this org" vs "global").

default_language.description:
Deprecated: kept for one release. Used to be `default_language` (int);
now accepts either int or string via LanguageRef. Prefer the explicit
fields above.
